{"tid":1444104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人發現到唔識散果一個問題","createTime":"2019-08-11T11:25:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T12:24:42.000Z","uid":84408,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"52e4dbaa287291fef91f5e428a1848bb70aa96e1","tid":1444104,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:25:49.000Z","msg":"由6月至今我地到8月開始識得打遊擊<br />\n但都仲係出現緊一打到夜晚<br />\n又開始打陣地或者唔識散嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n比如琴晚黃埔咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個係咪無得解決"},{"pid":"44675823e3387dfa1cf914fa7fe16a38ac621762","tid":1444104,"uid":131842,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:28:01.000Z","msg":"@11Aug 1926 <a href=\"https://hkmap.live/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkmap.live%2F&d=4z%2BvbskHrV%2FWTILUlLswqvsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=cdd9e065\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkmap.live/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/agyeQYD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FagyeQYD.png&h=f7e159cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkmap.live\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkmap.live&d=4z%2BvbskHrV%2FWTILUlLswqvsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=a9d38ac4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkmap.live</a><br />\n[長期置頂] [iOS/Android/PC/Mac] 香城online正式加入地圖功能<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438115\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438115</a><br />\n<br />\n覺得我地有用既 幫手宣傳去連登以外既地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dd9b369e36177d4548f293e3d13fc20a4d6c851","tid":1444104,"uid":65858,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:37:16.000Z","msg":"每一日都總會有一班手足係唔識走<br />\n黑警列曬隊 唔衝唔擲野唔轉場<br />\n企曬喺度食煙<br />\n見到黑警開始衝鋒又即刻掉頭叫人走 守都唔守一下<br />\n想斷後嘅手足一係俾同隊頂住走唔到 一係擰轉頭就冇曬人<br />\n結果每次都少幾個<br />\n<br />\n幾時先可以學到hit&amp;run<br />\nhit唔到咪轉個地方囉 唔好企曬喺度<br />\n<br />\n利申：純討論 扔核彈都唔割"},{"pid":"0d92374ff594ab5